== UMUGANURO ==

Buri uko umwaka utashe, mu Burundi haraba umusi mukuru wo kurya umwaka ariwo bita Umuganuro.

Uwo musi mukuru wahimbazwa mu kwezi kwa kigarama(kugira cumi na kabiri) ugatanguzwa n'Umwami ubwiwe. Uwo musi mukuru w'Umuganuro witabirirwa n'Abarundi bose kuko wari uhambaye cane.

             Akamaro k'Umuganuro

• Uguhezagira imbuto: Kuri uyo musi, Umwami yatanga umwaka w'Amasaka ariwo muganuro akaba atanze uruhusha rwo kuja kubiba amasaka(bavyita ko ahezagiye imbuto) Isoko: la fête des prémices au Burundi de Joseph RUGOMANA et F.M Rodegem.

•Kuraba abaganwa bakimuyoboka: Ku musi w'Umuganuro, abaganwa n'abatware Bose bategerezwa kurenguka Ku kirimba i bwangi. Iyo bishitse Umuganwa ntarenguke Kuri uyo musi, yafatwa nk'uwiyonkoye Ku mwami muri ico gihe yarakwa akarere Umwami Yaba yaramuhaye.

•Ukugaba n'ukuganza: Umusi w'Umuganuro wari umusi wo kunywanisha abarundi bo mu mihingo yose y'igihugu bikerekana ububasha bw'Umwami. Muri ivyo birori Umwami yaragaba Inka n'amatongo kubantu bitwaye neza.


